N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 496.4 - Procedure

State Regulations

The procedure to be followed in carrying out the
provisions as regards State civil defense organizations shall be in accordance
with the instructions of the State Civil Defense Commission. Notes
